    "publication_date": "2026-01-07",
    "description": "<p>Initial public release of de-identified dataset and analysis code for:\n\"Interferential current stimulation during dental facial treatment improves masticatory function\".<\/p>\n<p>What's included<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>data/processed/DFT_glucose.csv (mg/dL; long format, Pre/Post)<\/li>\n<li>data/processed/DFT_VAS.csv (mm; long format, Pre/Post)<\/li>\n<li>code/01_analysis.R (primary lmer + sensitivity tests; fixed seed)<\/li>\n<li>DATA_DICTIONARY.md, README.md, LICENSE-DATA (CC BY 4.0), LICENSE-CODE (MIT)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Reproducibility<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>R &gt;= 4.3; run <code>source(&quot;code/requirements.R&quot;)<\/code>, then <code>Rscript code/01_analysis.R<\/code><\/li>\n<li>Outputs saved to results/tables and results/figures<\/li>\n<\/ul>",
